-- BP Whiting Refinery Upgrade ‘On Track’ for Next Year, CEO Says
-- B y   J i m   P o l s o n   a n d   M a r i o   P a r k e r
-- 2012-01-13T18:53:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-13/bp-whiting-refinery-upgrade-on-track-for-next-year-ceo-says.html
BP Plc (BP/) ’s multibillion-dollar upgrade
of its Whiting refinery is “on track” to be done next year,
Chief Executive Officer  Robert Dudley  said.  Increasing output at the plant is the largest industrial
project in  Indiana ’s history, Dudley said at the Economic Club
of  Chicago  today.  To contact the reporters on this story:
